flowchart LR
  PREP[prepare] --> SUP{supervisor enabled}
  SUP -->|yes| SV[supervisor]
  SUP -->|no| SW[investigation_swarm]
  SV --> SW
  SW --> RF[reflector]
  RF --> PL[planner]
  PL --> PG[policy_gate]
  PG -->|approved| EX[executor]
  PG -->|approval pending or blocked| AG[aggregate]
  EX --> VF[verifier]
  VF --> AG
  AG --> END[END]
